Feature: Verify Login Module

Scenario Outline: User Login And Verify Select Hotel
	Given User on the OMR Branch Page
	When User enter "<username>" and "<password>"
	And User click login button 
	And User click HotelBooking  Option and fill all field "<state>","<city>","<roomtype>","<checkin>","<checkout>","<room>","<adults>","<child>"
				click search button
	Then User should verify selected hotel 
	
	Examples:
	
		|username|password|state|city|roomtype|checkin|checkout|room|adults|child|
		|keerthikakeerthuu@gmail.com|Keerthu18@|Tamil Nadu|Chennai|Deluxe|27|02|2|4|2|
	

Scenario Outline: With Mandatory filed and verify select hotel
	Given User on the OMR Branch Page
	When User enter "<username>" and "<password>"
	And User click login button 
	And User click HotelBooking  Option and fill all field "<state>","<city>","<checkin>","<checkout>","<room>","<adults>",
			and	click search button
	Then User should verify selected hotel 
	
	Examples:
	
		|username|password|state|city|checkin|checkout|room|adults|
		|keerthikakeerthuu@gmail.com|Keerthu18@|Tamil Nadu|Chennai|27|02|2|4|


Scenario Outline: Without Enter any Field 
	Given User on the OMR Branch Page
	When User enter "<username>" and "<password>"
	And User click login button 
	And User click HotelBooking  Option and without enter any field and click search button
	Then User should verify error msg "Please select state","Please select city","Please select Check-in date","Please select Check-out date","Please select no. of rooms","Please select no. of adults"


Scenario Outline: Select room type option verify ends with hotel name
	Given User on the OMR Branch Page
	When User enter "<username>" and "<password>"
	And User click login button 
	And User click HotelBooking  Option and select one room type "<state>","<city>","<roomtype>","<checkin>","<checkout>","<room>","<adults>","<child>"
	And user click search button
	Then User should Verify hotel name ends with room type
	
Examples:
	
		|username|password|state|city|roomtype|checkin|checkout|room|adults|child|
		|keerthikakeerthuu@gmail.com|Keerthu18@|Tamil Nadu|Chennai|Deluxe|27|02|2|4|2|


Scenario Outline: Select room type option verify ends with hotel name
	Given User on the OMR Branch Page
	When User enter "<username>" and "<password>"
	And User click login button 
	And User click HotelBooking  Option and fill all field with all room type "<state>","<city>","<roomtype>","<checkin>","<checkout>","<room>","<adults>","<child>"
	And user click search button
	Then User should verify header with "Standard/Deluxe/Suite/Luxury/Studio"
		
Examples:
	
		|username|password|state|city|roomtype|checkin|checkout|room|adults|child|
		|keerthikakeerthuu@gmail.com|Keerthu18@|Tamil Nadu|Chennai|Standard/Deluxe/Suite/Luxury/Studio|27|02|2|4|2|

	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	